name: Ai Puppet Master Series by Kevin Page

metadata.name: Ai Puppet Master Series #1-Dee-Dee Foss
metadata.description: The Ai Puppet Master Series is an exclusive Limited Edition PFP collection of Ai-generated artworks featuring hyper-realistic puppets created with a custom-trained Ai model by artist Kevin W. Page. Each unique character is available as an edition of five (5/1) and for a limited time.
